ScintillaQuick vendored Scintilla snapshot
==========================================

This directory contains a vendored copy of the Scintilla editing
component (https://www.scintilla.org/) imported for ScintillaQuick's
build. Only the subset of files that ScintillaQuick actually compiles
is committed here — Scintilla's lexers, documentation, test suite,
and build scripts are intentionally not part of the snapshot.

Upstream project: https://www.scintilla.org/
Upstream VCS:     https://sourceforge.net/projects/scintilla/ (Mercurial)
                  https://github.com/ScintillaOrg/lexilla (mirror; lexers)
License:          See ./LICENSE

Compatibility targets (library API used by ScintillaQuick):
  - ScintillaBase / Editor / EditView / MarginView / EditModel
  - Document / CellBuffer / ContractionState / PerLine / RunStyles
  - PositionCache / Style / ViewStyle / Selection / KeyMap
  - AutoComplete / CallTip / Indicator / LineMarker
  - CaseConvert / CaseFolder / CharacterCategoryMap / CharacterType
    / UniConversion / UniqueString / DBCS
  - Geometry / Platform / RESearch / ChangeHistory / Decoration / XPM

When updating this vendored snapshot:

  1. Record the new upstream tag or commit here along with the date
     of the import and the name of the person doing the update.
  2. Re-run the full test suite (ctest) on all supported platforms
     before committing the update.
  3. If Scintilla adds new SCI_* messages in the import, run the
     dispatch-table test (scintillaquick_dispatch_table_test) and
     classify any new messages that show up in the sweep.
  4. Update this file with the new version record.

